cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper involves the use of computer vision systems and unmanned aerial vehicles for terrain monitoring and mapping tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of path planning and uncertainty estimation, which falls under the categories of cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves the use of deep learning, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves the use of mapping, which falls under the category of cs.GR (Graphics).
